   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Raritan, a leader in the growing intelligent power market, would strengthen Legrand’s global leadership position and expand its reach and breadth of solutions for data center customers."
  },
  {
   "url": "https://www.raritan.com/about-us/newsroom/detail/legrand-revitalizes-data-center-sector-with-two-revolutionary-intelligent-rack-pdus",
   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Combining the best software and hardware technology from previous generations of Raritan and Server Technology rack PDUs while adding a considerable number of new, ground-breaking features"
  },
  {
